  "pluginNotes": "Carousel is a SAP instance. Plugin places it via SAP_KEYS. SAP Carousel ships with hardcoded sample pages that can't be easily replaced per-instance — for production specs, the plugin builds a native Auto Layout horizontal scroll container with the same paging dots styling.",
